24
00:02:11,970 --> 00:02:13,510
You may all leave.

25
00:02:14,882 --> 00:02:18,386
Ruo'xi, I have some things to say to you.

26
00:02:18,899 --> 00:02:20,640
After you were switched to washing clothes,

27
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:23,120
did you also wash your brains into a mess?

28
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,740
This is your best opportunity.

29
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,674
You need to grab it.

30
00:02:28,210 --> 00:02:30,398
If you do not grab it,

31
00:02:30,398 --> 00:02:32,409
even if I wanted to help you

32
00:02:32,409 --> 00:02:34,480
I wouldn't be able to.

33
00:02:34,849 --> 00:02:37,682
I know that Eunuch Li treats me well.

34
00:02:38,411 --> 00:02:40,282
I don't dare to do it again.

35
00:02:42,372 --> 00:02:46,412
In the Palace, you are a smart person.

36
00:02:46,412 --> 00:02:49,803
This time, even though I made the decision privately,

37
00:02:49,803 --> 00:02:53,378
I could not do that without the Emperor's special favor.

38
00:02:54,307 --> 00:02:57,558
You must not continue in doing the wrong thing.

39
00:02:58,394 --> 00:02:59,416
Yes.

40
00:03:02,829 --> 00:03:05,520
I have a question in my heart,

41
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:08,216
but I don't know if I can ask  Eunuch Li.

42
00:03:08,913 --> 00:03:10,259
You may ask.

43
00:03:10,659 --> 00:03:13,928
Eunuch Li has always understood the Emperor's thoughts.

44
00:03:13,928 --> 00:03:15,368
Do you think

45
00:03:15,368 --> 00:03:17,550
the person that HIs Majesty supports in his heart

46
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:20,340
is the 4th Prince or the 14th Prince?

47
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:23,713
I just said that you needed to be careful in your actions and words.

48
00:03:23,713 --> 00:03:26,720
Did you even hear what I said?

49
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,574
I already said we are servants.

50
00:03:32,574 --> 00:03:34,849
We can't get involved with Palace issues.

51
00:03:34,849 --> 00:03:36,753
Even if you let me guess

52
00:03:36,753 --> 00:03:39,122
I do not have a clear answer.

53
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:43,278
Both brothers are doted on by the Emperor.

54
00:03:43,278 --> 00:03:46,622
Also the Emperor has said before

55
00:03:46,622 --> 00:03:50,105
everything is under his control.

56
00:03:50,105 --> 00:03:53,054
All this time, in order to suppress any struggles,

57
00:03:53,054 --> 00:03:54,920
he has decided not to appoint a Crown Prince.

58
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,783
Not until the very last moment,

59
00:03:56,783 --> 00:04:00,809
will the Emperor announce who the successor is.

60
00:04:01,809 --> 00:04:04,617
Your Majesty, please look after your health.

61
00:04:04,617 --> 00:04:07,357
Don't tire yourself out so much.

62
00:04:08,432 --> 00:04:11,412
As long as I can see the country prosper and the common people at peace,

63
00:04:11,683 --> 00:04:14,145
that they have food to eat and clothes to wear,

64
00:04:14,145 --> 00:04:16,645
it does not matter how tired I am, it is worthy.

65
00:04:16,645 --> 00:04:17,899
However, I

66
00:04:17,899 --> 00:04:20,267
could not help the Emperor with his worries.

67
00:04:21,963 --> 00:04:24,656
You already helped me

68
00:04:24,835 --> 00:04:26,699
All these years,

69
00:04:26,699 --> 00:04:29,864
you have served me dutifully

70
00:04:29,864 --> 00:04:32,644
and I am completely aware of it.

71
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:36,243
I would not dare to create trouble for the Emperor.

72
00:04:37,164 --> 00:04:39,540
I only hoped 14th Prince

73
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:42,001
could come back earlier

74
00:04:42,001 --> 00:04:45,949
so the Emperor can feel relieved.

75
00:04:45,949 --> 00:04:48,549
The 14th prince is braver than other people.

76
00:04:48,549 --> 00:04:50,871
I am confident in him.

77
00:04:50,871 --> 00:04:55,097
This is all due to your contribution.

78
00:04:55,097 --> 00:04:57,234
I could not dare to accept the credit.

79
00:04:57,932 --> 00:05:00,090
I only hope that 4th Prince

80
00:05:00,090 --> 00:05:01,506
and 14th Prince

81
00:05:01,506 --> 00:05:03,424
can help Your Majesty with his worries and issues,

82
00:05:03,424 --> 00:05:06,443
then I will be satisfied.

83
00:05:07,358 --> 00:05:09,122
Out of these two brothers,

84
00:05:09,122 --> 00:05:11,840
which one do you favor?

85
00:05:13,302 --> 00:05:14,741
The two of them

86
00:05:14,741 --> 00:05:16,831
are both my sons.

87
00:05:16,831 --> 00:05:19,060
There is no difference.

88
00:05:19,318 --> 00:05:21,197
To me,

89
00:05:21,197 --> 00:05:25,307
you are stricter with the 4th Prince.

90
00:05:25,307 --> 00:05:26,328
That's right.

91
00:05:26,528 --> 00:05:28,040
I only wish

92
00:05:28,443 --> 00:05:32,458
he can be a good role model for 14th Prince.

93
00:05:32,616 --> 00:05:34,200
Did you know

94
00:05:35,268 --> 00:05:37,497
sometimes I suspected

95
00:05:38,008 --> 00:05:41,352
that silent and reticent character of 4th Prince,

96
00:05:41,523 --> 00:05:43,120
just because you

97
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,903
were so strict with him.

98
00:05:45,903 --> 00:05:47,575
Your Majesty!

99
00:05:48,225 --> 00:05:49,840
My skill of guidance is lacking

100
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,708
and I caused torment in the princes.

101
00:05:51,708 --> 00:05:54,448
There can not be enough punishment for me.

102
00:05:54,448 --> 00:05:56,080
Don't talk about faults.

103
00:05:56,616 --> 00:05:58,840
As a father,

104
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:02,041
my fault is even greater.

105
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:05,431
Well.  The Emperor handles tens of thousands of matters each day,

106
00:06:05,431 --> 00:06:07,546
who has that much time?

107
00:06:07,546 --> 00:06:09,192
That is why

108
00:06:09,192 --> 00:06:11,886
if the child was not bought up right, it was the father's fault.

109
00:06:13,497 --> 00:06:16,808
Unfortunately, the ruler of a country

110
00:06:16,808 --> 00:06:18,062
can not be the same as

111
00:06:18,805 --> 00:06:21,160
a regular person.

112
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:25,720
Going out to work after sunrise and coming home for rest after sunset.

113
00:06:26,352 --> 00:06:27,722
Every night

114
00:06:27,722 --> 00:06:29,758
sitting under a big tree,

115
00:06:29,758 --> 00:06:33,155
they can accompany their children, cool off, and tell stories.

116
00:06:36,592 --> 00:06:41,250
Sometimes, if one of them was sick

117
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:43,929
I couldn't even go to see him.

118
00:06:45,462 --> 00:06:48,016
The princes will understand.

119
00:06:49,967 --> 00:06:53,578
There are times where I can not be clear.

120
00:06:53,578 --> 00:06:57,249
Do they truly have filial piety towards me

121
00:06:57,977 --> 00:07:01,893
or is it because of the Emperor's throne?

122
00:07:01,893 --> 00:07:07,312
Your Majesty, the way the princes treat you is real.

123
00:07:08,217 --> 00:07:10,725
A man at birth, is fundamentally good in nature.

124
00:07:10,725 --> 00:07:13,776
Moreover, Emperor treats them nicely

125
00:07:13,776 --> 00:07:15,137
and

126
00:07:15,137 --> 00:07:18,156
Emperor makes a pain staking effort to cultivate them.

127
00:07:18,156 --> 00:07:19,781
At times like this,

128
00:07:21,088 --> 00:07:25,000
whether real or pretense, both are good,

129
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,700
I do not care.

130
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:31,955
I only care about their future.

131
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:40,920
They are all my own blood and flesh,

132
00:07:44,835 --> 00:07:47,204
I really hope

133
00:07:49,201 --> 00:07:52,120
the brothers won't destroy each other.

134
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:57,320
I, Long Ke Duo, humbly greets the Emperor.

135
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:00,098
Rise.

136
00:08:00,098 --> 00:08:01,560
Thank you, Your Majesty.

137
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,400
I am getting old.

138
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:12,899
Today, I am also ill.

139
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:16,020
Blessing the Emperor with a long life and good fortune.

140
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:21,312
I plan on having 14th Prince return.

141
00:08:21,312 --> 00:08:23,620
When he returns this time,

142
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:27,800
I don't plan on having him return to the battlefield.

143
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:31,368
Therefore, I need to pick someone to replace him.

144
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:34,851
We must think carefully.

145
00:08:34,851 --> 00:08:37,120
We cannot be too hasty in making this decision.

146
00:08:38,063 --> 00:08:40,430
The Emperor, please look after your health.

147
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:43,062
Bring a cup of tea.

148
00:08:46,277 --> 00:08:49,696
Do you have someone on your mind?

149
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:32,880
Sister, what's wrong?

150
00:09:34,457 --> 00:09:37,320
Go and bring His Majesty a cup of tea.

151
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:48,505
Emotionally, I hope it will not happen.

152
00:09:48,505 --> 00:09:51,960
I do not want 4th Prince to be upset, disappointed, or  in pain.

153
00:09:53,065 --> 00:09:54,387
But rationally,

154
00:09:54,387 --> 00:09:57,520
I think that it is the best solution to everything.

155
00:09:57,862 --> 00:10:00,045
If 14th Prince steps up to the throne,

156
00:10:00,045 --> 00:10:03,110
everyone might still remain alive.

157
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:05,080
If 14th prince becomes Emperor,

158
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:08,544
will he really not kill those brothers who were not on his side?

159
00:10:08,544 --> 00:10:10,448
Hurry, hurry!

160
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:41,060
Has one of the greatest Emperors

161
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:44,743
finally reached the end of his life?

162
00:10:52,036 --> 00:10:53,200
Come.

163
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,448
Yes.

164
00:10:55,448 --> 00:10:56,860
Send this order out.

165
00:10:56,860 --> 00:11:00,269
Immediately send in a large troop to surround Qian'qin Palace.

166
00:11:00,269 --> 00:11:02,112
Without my permission,

167
00:11:02,112 --> 00:11:04,000
no one can enter or leave.

168
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,180
Use my name badge to send out the order.

169
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:08,140
Impose martial law on all 9 Gates.

170
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:10,740
Whether Imperial Prince or Qin'wang,
(Qin'wang -   Prince of the First Rank, highest rank, Bei'le is 4th )

171
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:12,340
without my permission,

172
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:14,120
is forbidden to leave or enter privately.

173
00:11:15,115 --> 00:11:16,400
Yes.

174
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,960
Eunuch Li.

175
00:11:23,614 --> 00:11:27,880
Do you think... my arrangement... is complete?

176
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:31,560
Your arrangement is indeed reasonable and fair.

177
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:35,000
Send people to pass the order on.

178
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,760
No one can leave without permission.

179
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:40,616
No one can approach without permission.

180
00:11:40,616 --> 00:11:43,265
Whoever violates this order will be beaten to death right away!

181
00:11:43,265 --> 00:11:44,426
Understood.

182
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:55,020
I already ordered someone to draft the decree

183
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:58,080
to pass the throne to 14th prince.

184
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:03,761
Later on you will assist him with all your heart.

185
00:12:03,761 --> 00:12:09,160
静 (calm, peace)

186
00:12:17,452 --> 00:12:19,100
Wang'ye we got news from the palace.

187
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,020
The Emperor's illness has become most urgent.

188
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:23,568
Right now the inside and outside of Qian'qin Palace is sealed.  No one can go in or come out.

189
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:25,500
You may leave.

190
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,865
Yes.

191
00:12:47,965 --> 00:12:52,537
The win or loss of so many years of hard work will have all been determined by now.

192
00:12:54,264 --> 00:12:55,983
Prepare to enter the palace.

193
00:12:57,655 --> 00:13:02,299
行動 (action)

194
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:57,569
His Imperial Majesty has passed away

195
00:13:57,569 --> 00:13:58,862
Your Majesty!

196
00:13:59,162 --> 00:14:03,088
Your Majesty!

197
00:14:07,161 --> 00:14:09,009
The Emperor was just telling me

198
00:14:09,009 --> 00:14:11,146
the decree had already been drafted

199
00:14:11,146 --> 00:14:13,050
and the throne is to be passed on to the 4th Prince,

200
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:15,047
when suddenly he fainted!

201
00:14:15,247 --> 00:14:21,316
I didn't imagine it. Your Majesty!

202
00:15:03,332 --> 00:15:07,275
Before the Emperor passed away, he already instructed me (with these words):

203
00:15:07,275 --> 00:15:09,683
"The 4th Prince is noble

204
00:15:09,683 --> 00:15:11,340
and is really similiar to me.

205
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:13,895
He will inherit the throne

206
00:15:13,895 --> 00:15:15,945
Therefore, he will ascend the throne in the next few days

207
00:15:15,945 --> 00:15:18,600
and he will be the new Emperor."

208
00:15:21,829 --> 00:15:25,008
Greetings to Your Majesty!

209
00:15:36,147 --> 00:15:38,012
Greetings to Your Majesty!

210
00:15:38,012 --> 00:15:40,798
Greetings to Your Majesty.

211
00:15:50,791 --> 00:15:53,592
Greetings to Your Majesty.

212
00:16:11,743 --> 00:16:14,397
Restrict everyone separately.

213
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:17,857
Do not allow anyone to approach privately or spread the news.

214
00:16:17,857 --> 00:16:19,257
Understood.

215
00:16:27,586 --> 00:16:29,304
Maiden.  Please.

216
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:58,515
This way is good too.

217
00:16:59,344 --> 00:17:01,673
I will not witness

218
00:17:01,673 --> 00:17:05,620
the final conflict right before he ascends the throne.

219
00:17:20,583 --> 00:17:23,986
The former Emperor has passed away.  The whole country is in mourning

220
00:17:23,986 --> 00:17:27,520
I beg Your Majesty to take care of yourself

221
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:29,328
Please, for the sake of the country,

222
00:17:29,328 --> 00:17:31,000
quickly chose an auspicious day to be enthroned,

223
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,322
so the whole country can be notified

224
00:17:32,322 --> 00:17:34,181
to show our Qing Dynasty's prosperity

225
00:17:34,181 --> 00:17:36,131
and show Your Majesty's heavenly grace.

226
00:17:36,248 --> 00:17:38,895
The most important thing right now is the funeral arrangement for the former Emperor.

227
00:17:38,895 --> 00:17:42,099
We can talk about ascending the throne later.

228
00:17:42,921 --> 00:17:45,837
Emperor.  This is of utmost importance.

229
00:17:45,837 --> 00:17:48,624
Even though our Qing Dynasty is at its peak,

230
00:17:48,624 --> 00:17:50,806
the countries surrounding us all have their own ambitions.

231
00:17:50,806 --> 00:17:52,757
They want to invade us at any given opportunity.

232
00:17:52,757 --> 00:17:55,080
Right now, the former Emperor has suddenly died.

233
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:57,401
Our enemies of long standing have been waiting for it.

234
00:17:57,401 --> 00:18:00,884
If Your Majesty does not ascend the throne and spread notification everywhere, there will be no official ruler.

235
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:04,135
That will cause the country not to be at peace.

236
00:18:04,413 --> 00:18:06,560
I agree with that suggestion also.  Your Majesty,

237
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,989
the great Qing Dynasty could not be without an Emperor for even one day.

238
00:18:07,989 --> 00:18:10,543
I beg Your Majesty to put aside your grief

239
00:18:10,543 --> 00:18:12,447
and ascend the throne as soon as possible.

240
00:18:12,447 --> 00:18:13,960
I agree also.

241
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:17,480
Right now, the Ministry of (Confucian) Rites has already posted the former Emperor's posthumous decree to the whole country.

242
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:19,437
Everyone under the heavens knows.

243
00:18:19,437 --> 00:18:22,827
I beg Your Majesty to make an immediate decision

244
00:18:22,827 --> 00:18:25,009
to reassure and stabalize the common people's minds.

245
00:18:26,263 --> 00:18:31,000
We beg Your Majesty to chose an auspicious day to ascend the throne.

246
00:19:16,558 --> 00:19:18,276
Fourth Brother.

247
00:19:20,226 --> 00:19:24,127
How dare you! Bei'le, you should call him the Emperor

248
00:19:24,127 --> 00:19:25,980
How could you lack manners in front of the Emperor?

249
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:27,660
You should immediately kneel down and ask for forgiveness.

250
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,860
How dare you!  Bei'le'ye

251
00:19:29,860 --> 00:19:31,953
is not some servant like you that can be cursed at--

252
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:34,003
Eighth Brother!

253
00:19:37,223 --> 00:19:39,660
I don't know what 4th Brother has discussed here.

254
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,775
But why did you not notify all our brothers

255
00:19:41,775 --> 00:19:43,307
and discuss it together?

256
00:19:44,933 --> 00:19:47,726
I am talking about the funeral arrangement for the former Emperor.

257
00:19:49,159 --> 00:19:51,806
Are you also talking about a fake Imperial order to get the throne

258
00:19:51,806 --> 00:19:54,499
and the attempt to be Emperor?

259
00:19:55,149 --> 00:19:59,700
9th Brother.  How could you talk rubbish about the posthumous decree of the former Emperor?

260
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:02,115
Fourth Brother.

261
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:05,087
You usually focus on farming and the colors of spring,

262
00:20:05,213 --> 00:20:07,177
if the posthumous decree stated that

263
00:20:07,177 --> 00:20:10,242
you were given one hundred acres of good farm land,. I could believe that

264
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:12,657
But if the decree states the throne is to be passed to you,

265
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,940
then that may be in jest.

266
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,558
If you say another absurd word,

267
00:20:16,558 --> 00:20:18,680
do not blame me for not honoring our brotherhood.

268
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,227
What can you do?!

269
00:20:23,733 --> 00:20:25,460
The day that Imperial Father passed away,

270
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:26,840
all of us

271
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,749
were blocked outside of the Emperor's palace.

272
00:20:28,949 --> 00:20:31,520
