273
00:20:33,207 --> 00:20:36,460
Not sure how on that day you were here

274
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,180
or how you persuaded Imperial Father to pass the throne to an

275
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:40,869
unconcerned person who treated farming as a pleasant pastime.

276
00:20:41,566 --> 00:20:45,746
The former Emperor made a determination a long time ago regarding his successor.

277
00:20:45,746 --> 00:20:49,275
He would not be persuaded by others in a few sentences.

278
00:20:49,454 --> 00:20:50,960
While Imperial Father was still alive

279
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:53,199
