281
00:20:56,311 --> 00:20:57,890
Everyone in the Imperial Court,

282
00:20:57,890 --> 00:20:59,480
and us brothers alike,

283
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,280
had all took note of that.

284
00:21:01,551 --> 00:21:05,060
The intention of Imperial Father was understood without saying.

285
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:06,442
So I ask...

286
00:21:06,442 --> 00:21:08,600
how could Imperial Father during his end time

287
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,440
so suddenly change?

288
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,965
Fourteenth Brother is so extremely talented

289
00:21:13,965 --> 00:21:16,287
he can be called the model among all princes.

290
00:21:16,287 --> 00:21:18,160
I am very happy about that too.

291
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,731
I will entrust him with heavy responsibilities.

292
00:21:20,731 --> 00:21:24,128
I already told our 14th Brother to come back for the funeral.

293
00:21:25,057 --> 00:21:28,000
Therefore, you have no need to use his name when you question me.

294
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,680
Li De Chuan.

295
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,800
Your servant is here

296
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:36,640
Since all the Bei'le and Bei'zi have doubts in their minds
(Princely Ranks)

297
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:39,120
you should read the posthumous decree aloud again in public.

298
00:21:39,120 --> 00:21:40,560
Yes.

299
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:45,955
The former Emperor personally said:

300
00:21:45,955 --> 00:21:48,640
"4th Prince is noble

301
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,360
and is really similar to me.

302
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:52,760
He will inherit the throne.

303
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:55,200
Therefore, he will ascend the throne in the next few days

304
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:57,100
and become the new Emperor."

305
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:59,005
Li De Chuan!

306
00:21:59,005 --> 00:22:00,760
You bastard servant!

307
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,859
Didn't my Imperial Father treat you well when he was alive?

308
00:22:02,859 --> 00:22:05,111
However you dare to fake an Imperial order and help a usurper!

309
00:22:05,111 --> 00:22:06,737
What you did is contrary to Imperial Father's wishes.

310
00:22:06,737 --> 00:22:08,200
That day, several of us were not there.

311
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,877
The posthumous decree in your hand... no one knows whether it is real or a fake!

312
00:22:10,877 --> 00:22:13,040
If you wish for us to willingly kneel down to you and be your servants based on that decree

313
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,971
is impossible!

314
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:22,400
That day both I and Eunuch Li

315
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:25,127
were both witnesses standing right next to the former Emperor.

316
00:22:25,127 --> 00:22:27,040
I, as a Nine Gate ti'du
(Ti Du - Local Commander)

317
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:28,480
entrusted by the former Emperor

318
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:30,400
with guarding the Qian'qin Palace and the former Emperor,

319
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,300
how then could I falsify--

320
00:22:31,300 --> 00:22:32,363
Shut up!

321
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:34,600
Imperial Father could have been confused by you.

322
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:37,000
However, do not think that we do not know of your background.

323
00:22:46,327 --> 00:22:48,560
Your servant, Nian Geng Yao, returns to protect the Emperor.

324
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:50,785
Greetings to the Emperor.

325
00:22:51,342 --> 00:22:55,360
- Greetings to the Emperor.
- Greetings to the Emperor.

326
00:23:04,345 --> 00:23:05,700
All rise.

327
00:23:05,700 --> 00:23:07,800
- Gratitude to His Majesty.
- Gratitude to His Majesty.

328
00:23:14,771 --> 00:23:15,820
While the whole country is in mourning

329
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:17,420
I can understand your feelings.

330
00:23:17,420 --> 00:23:18,840
But the most important thing now

331
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:19,980
is the funeral arrangement for the former Emperor

332
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:21,505
and as for the other Imperial matters...

333
00:23:22,280 --> 00:23:23,900
From this day on,

334
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:27,500
General Ma, Long Ke Duo,

335
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:30,282
8th Brother, and also 13th Brother

336
00:23:30,282 --> 00:23:32,751
are the Prime Ministers.

337
00:23:32,851 --> 00:23:34,180
I confer these titles. 8th Prince,

338
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:36,125
the title of He'shuo'lian Qinwang.
(Blood Prince of the First Rank, Lian - his new name )

339
00:23:36,125 --> 00:23:39,460
13th Prince the title of He'shuo'yi Qin'wang.
(Also Blood Prince of the First Rank, Yi - his same name )

340
00:23:39,460 --> 00:23:41,880
I hope everyone will cooperate with me

341
00:23:42,658 --> 00:23:44,040
while we go through this difficult time together.

342
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,560
- We receive the order and thank Your Majesty.
- We receive the order and thank Your Majesty.

343
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:09,894
I accept the order and thank His Majesty.

344
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:32,380
8th Brother.  How could you just kneel down when you were just given a Qing'wan.

345
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,360
Then our brother

346
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:35,396
couldn't contest again for you!

347
00:24:35,396 --> 00:24:36,840
Contest?

348
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,695
I originally thought that

349
00:24:38,695 --> 00:24:40,421
the attitude of Imperial Father was obvious, that

350
00:24:40,521 --> 00:24:43,040
14th Brother definitely would be the successor

351
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:44,693
