352
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:49,191
Who knew that in just one night, that dream would be in vain.

353
00:24:49,191 --> 00:24:52,720
The Imperial throne is now in 4th Brother's hand with a blink of an eye.

354
00:24:53,138 --> 00:24:54,160
That's right, Eighth Brother.

355
00:24:54,485 --> 00:24:55,480
I really don't understand

356
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:57,520
how you could let it go?

357
00:24:57,520 --> 00:24:59,080
You are really giving the Imperial throne

358
00:24:59,080 --> 00:25:01,040
away.

359
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:04,740
We do not have any control over an army in the capital city.

360
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:07,974
It is already difficult enough to deal with Long Ke Duo.

361
00:25:07,974 --> 00:25:10,120
Now that Nian Gen Yao is also here,

362
00:25:10,328 --> 00:25:13,718
which of you can withstand him?

363
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:16,240
The most important thing is

364
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:18,560
Long Ke Duo has the oral instruction of Imperial Father

365
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,440
and has Li De Quan as a witness.

366
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:23,935
Now that posthumous decree has been declared all over the country,

367
00:25:24,135 --> 00:25:26,640
unless we have the intention of rebelling,

368
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,997
we do not have the ability to turn it around.

369
00:25:31,260 --> 00:25:33,662
You two need not worry.

370
00:25:33,662 --> 00:25:36,636
4th Prince may have controlled the key moment this time,

371
00:25:36,636 --> 00:25:39,040
but it is still not right and proper.

372
00:25:39,439 --> 00:25:42,800
We will have an opportunity in the future to push him off the throne.

373
00:25:43,525 --> 00:25:45,320
The strategy now

374
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:48,269
is restrain action and wait until we have that opportunity.

375
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:52,320
De Fei was always more fond of 14th Brother

376
00:25:52,320 --> 00:25:54,220
and she is the birth mother of 4th Brother too.

377
00:25:54,220 --> 00:25:59,400
4th Brother will have a hard time dealing with his own Empress Dowager.

378
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:06,620
Niang Niang, please don't worry anymore. (Queen Mother)

379
00:26:06,620 --> 00:26:08,800
Please look after your health.

380
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:19,580
Invite Fourth Prince in.

381
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:21,280
Yes.

382
00:26:22,980 --> 00:26:24,020
Greetings to Your Majesty.

383
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:25,200
Excused.

384
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,480
Thank you, Your Majesty.

385
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,540
You may leave.

386
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:37,080
Mother asked me to come right away,

387
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:39,000
what is it for?

388
00:26:39,660 --> 00:26:43,720
4th Prince. Tell me the truth.

389
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:47,880
Did you really fake the posthumous decree?

390
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:50,280
When your Imperial Father was alive,

391
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:52,960
he really liked your 14th Brother.

392
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,600
He would never have

393
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:59,320
passed the throne down to you!

394
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:06,820
I and 14th Prince

395
00:27:06,820 --> 00:27:08,720
were both given birth by you.

396
00:27:09,220 --> 00:27:13,069
It does not matter which of us ascends to the throne, you will still be titled, Empress Dowager.

397
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:16,700
Mother, why do you favor 14th Brother more?

398
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:20,104
You really believe that I wouldn't be a good Emperor?

399
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:34,560
I am your Imperial Father's concubine.

400
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:38,495
Therefore, I need to follow the former Emperor's posthumous wishes.

401
00:27:38,495 --> 00:27:43,400
Whether your Imperial Father gave the thrown to my own son

402
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,960
or not, I still speak for him.

403
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:51,080
The former Emperor really did speak the order personally.

404
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:55,817
The Imperial Throne belongs to me.  It is right and proper

405
00:27:58,780 --> 00:28:01,340
Right and proper?

406
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:04,280
Is it really right and proper?

407
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:07,619
Your heart knows better than anyone else"s.

408
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:13,180
Even though I have not ascended to the throne yet,

409
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:16,320
I am already the real Emperor of the Qing Dynasty!

410
00:28:17,172 --> 00:28:19,800
Today, I would like to tell you,

411
00:28:21,251 --> 00:28:25,520
even though everyone sees you as the Emperor,

412
00:28:26,128 --> 00:28:31,343
I don't consider you deserving of it.

413
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,460
I was only detained for seven days,

414
00:29:48,460 --> 00:29:50,988
and I can't stand it much longer.

415
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:53,560
For 10 years, 13th Prince hasn't had any freedom,

416
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:56,096
how did he get through it?

417
00:29:59,045 --> 00:30:00,720
4th Prince ascended to the throne.

418
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:03,840
13th Prince will definitely be released

419
00:30:03,840 --> 00:30:06,520
and I will finally see him again.

420
00:30:16,321 --> 00:30:20,800
Lady, please follow me back to the palace.

421
00:30:33,085 --> 00:30:35,320
Has the Emperor had his coronation ceremony?

422
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:36,560
Replying to the Lady.

423
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:38,680
Today the Enthronement Ceremony was just finished.

424
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:41,440
His title was also announced to the country

425
00:30:41,816 --> 00:30:43,440
What about the 8th Prince and his people?

426
00:30:43,938 --> 00:30:45,080
Congratulations, Lady.

427
00:30:45,540 --> 00:30:48,420
The Emperor has already ordered the 8th Prince to be promoted to Qinwang.

428
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:50,120
Eighth Prince, Thirteenth Prince,

429
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,980
General Ma, and General Long,

430
00:30:51,980 --> 00:30:53,380
all four of them are now Prime Ministers.

431
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:55,230
The Emperor relies on 8th Prince.

432
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:57,140
Is 13th Prince well?

433
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:58,481
Very well.

434
00:30:58,481 --> 00:31:00,500
You will be able to see him soon.

435
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:02,475
These last several days, 8th Prince and 13th Prince

436
00:31:02,475 --> 00:31:05,140
have been discussing Imperial matters with the Emperor at Yang'xin Palace every day.

437
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:07,460
The Emperor treats 13th Prince very differently.

438
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:09,880
Because of the taboo, all of the other princes need to avoid using the Emperor's name,

439
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:11,820
so they all changed their own names,

440
00:31:12,580 --> 00:31:14,460
except for the 13th Prince.

441
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:16,801
The Emperor ordered the 13th Prince not to change his name.

442
00:31:16,801 --> 00:31:18,860
However, 13th Prince knelt down and declined.

443
00:31:18,860 --> 00:31:22,640
The Emperor really treats 13th Prince generously.

444
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,180
I know.

445
00:31:24,180 --> 00:31:25,980
You know?

446
00:31:48,173 --> 00:31:49,774
Only seven days.

447
00:31:49,774 --> 00:31:54,380
Only seven days and the Forbidden City has already changed owners.

448
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:26,508
I was doted on by the former Emperor for many years

449
00:32:26,508 --> 00:32:29,805
but I betrayed him for the 4th Prince.

450
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:33,860
Do I really obsess over the Forbidden City?

451
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:38,180
This may be the 4th Prince's dream

452
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:41,300
