453
00:33:03,020 --> 00:33:05,169
Let's stand up now.

454
00:33:06,641 --> 00:33:11,420
The Emperor asked me to escort you back.

455
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,800
13th Prince...

456
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:27,019
Rouxi has not groomed herself for seven days.

457
00:33:27,019 --> 00:33:29,180
My hair is messy and my face is dirty.

458
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:31,060
