462
00:34:23,304 --> 00:34:24,720
Your servant, Mei Xiang.

463
00:34:24,720 --> 00:34:25,979
Your servant,Ju Yun.

464
00:34:25,979 --> 00:34:27,120
- Greetings Lady.
- Greetings Lady.

465
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:29,002
- Greetings Lady Rouxi.
- Greetings Lady Rouxi.

466
00:34:29,002 --> 00:34:30,719
Please rise.

467
00:34:32,067 --> 00:34:33,420
Is Yutan still in the Palace?

468
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:35,220
Your servant doesn't know.

469
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,419
What about Wang Xi?

470
00:34:36,419 --> 00:34:37,720
Eunuch Wang is still here.

471
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:41,259
Would you mind finding Eunuch Wang for me?

472
00:34:41,259 --> 00:34:42,539
Yes.

473
00:34:43,031 --> 00:34:45,385
My Lady. Please wash face and rinse mouth first.

474
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:47,197
Alright.

475
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,980
Jie'jie.
(Elder Sister)

476
00:35:02,151 --> 00:35:04,659
