481
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:17,200
so I am also in service to the Yangxin Palace.

482
00:35:19,009 --> 00:35:20,680
What about Yutan?

483
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:22,840
Yutan, having already attained the age limit, is to be released from the palace.

484
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:24,160
The Emperor has pardoned her

485
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:26,920
to allow her to leave the Palace.

486
00:35:28,436 --> 00:35:30,660
Please tell her to come and see me.

487
00:35:30,660 --> 00:35:33,660
This, your servant cannot do.

488
00:35:34,620 --> 00:35:35,800
You may leave.

489
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:37,580
Yes.

490
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:52,220
You two may leave.

491
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:54,220
- Yes.
- Yes.

492
00:36:21,749 --> 00:36:24,500
What am I afraid of?

493
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:27,020
How long can I put this off?

494
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:30,420
When I couldn't see him, I yearned for him.

495
00:36:30,420 --> 00:36:35,797
Yet now, when I can see him, I cannot wait to run away.

496
00:37:14,807 --> 00:37:17,380
You're awake, why pretend to be sleeping?

497
00:37:18,708 --> 00:37:20,880
