501
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:45,740
I just want to lay next to you. Is that fine with you?

502
00:38:10,697 --> 00:38:15,220
This moment is what I had hoped for a very long time.

503
00:38:15,220 --> 00:38:17,220
Just the two of us.

504
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:19,540
Belonging to each other.

505
00:38:20,057 --> 00:38:24,288
What's in the past remains the past.

506
00:38:24,288 --> 00:38:26,020
Ruo'xi!

507
00:38:26,620 --> 00:38:28,460
I am here.

508
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:33,400
